<br>
Well ive been at this camp at lvl 55, 56 and now 60% into 57. <br>
<br>
If you dont wanna take out SSralm, the iksar monk,you can pull the prisoners as long as you dont pull the cells facing the same way as ZO. And you have to pull them so they always run clockwise around the block. The right entrance is far enough from Ssralm´s cell and therefor dont aggro him. <br>
<br>
This only applies to the prisoners and rats. Not sentrys who run all over and cant be trusted. <br>
<br>
Another thing. If both the hallways at ZO are camped, you can set up camp downstairs (from where you come from when Zoning in). Easy to fight there, and never adds or trains unless pulled there. But dont pull prisoners here if ssralm is up. This door is too close to his cell, and he will come too.<br>
<br>
I always pull with cancel magic or malosi. Target the mob, and walk away some. Cast CM or Mal then run all the way back to pet who is guarding at ZO or donwstairs. Then chaincast 51 or 57 earth with a ds wich is a very safe way and manaeffective. Just keep and eye on the malachite suppy. But lately ive gone the nuking way instead. Pull prisoner, send pet, sit down 10sec, let pet root once or twice. Stand up. Mob should be down to 80% by now. Cast sirocco, and as soon as the 2nd wave blast..cast Char and is will explode right after the 3rd wave of the sirocco. Mob is now down to 10% or less. If not, cast char again, and sit. Mob dead. <br>
<br>
At 57 i can kill 3 or 4 prisoners in about 2min, the nuking way before OOM. With kei im FOM again in 6-7min. Then do it again. 2 mobs give 1% lvl at 57. So around 2% of lvl in 10min. 4% (1 blue) in 20min. Yellow in 100min and the whole lvl 57 in 500min wich equals to 8,3 hours. <br>
<br>
Ofcourse I can only do this now at 57 when ive learned everything about this spot..the hard way. Before you learn it, you will get adds and trains. And do other mistakes. But when you have mastered it, the time schedule above can really be kept.<br>
