<br>
Yes, I very much disagree <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Canni = downtime = less xp for time played.  Plus the fact that, even if you're like me and carry around 3 bags of malachite, you can burn through that pretty fast if you need to canni all the time.  Then you have to go buy more which = even more downtime.  Even 57 earth has problems soloing most of these mobs, so my guess is that you'd need to re-summon after every 1-2 kills anyway PLUS canni up every 3 or 4(?).<br>
<br>
Whoever was asking about 59 air, it kinda sux on these imo.  Mostly because they end up running out into the hall at low hp and bringing rats.  You could nuke and kill them before they get there, but, well that takes more mana than necessary which = potential downtime.  Earth is the best way to go.<br>
<br>
Once you get this down you can very easily do 3 blues per hour regular xp before 59.  I just got a burnt wood staff the other day which makes xp go even a tad faster than that.  BW staff + horse = good <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
